Package org.sqlproc.engine.impl

Class SqlType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sqlproc.engine.impl.SqlType
  • class SqlType
extends Object
    The SQL type of a dynamic input value (SQL statement parameter) or an output value (SQL query scalar).
    Author:
    Vladimir Hudec
